{"lemma":"مِنَحِ","slug":"مِنَحِ","root":"م.ن.ح","root_slug":"م-ن-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/م-ن-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n38953","n38959"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gift"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"additional money given to the employees; bonus, allowance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"subsidy, monetary aid, financial support"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"scholarship, study grant"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Related to مَنَحَ (manaḥa, “to award, to grant, to bestow”). Compare Hebrew מִנְחָה (minḥā, “offering”)."},"ipa":["/min.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n38953","headword_ar":"مَنَحَهُ","root":"mnH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHN","text_ar":"مَنْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lent him"},{"kind":"text","text":"a she-camel, and a sheep or goat; (L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he might have the milk thereof, and return the animal after a certain period:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the original signification: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lent to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"a she-camel,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assigning to him her soft hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabar","text_ar":"وَبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and milk and offspring:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, L, K:) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lent him"},{"kind":"text","text":"a piece of land,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he might cultivate it and have the produce thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lent him"},{"kind":"text","text":"money or the like,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be repaid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaHahu","text_ar":"مَنَحَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHN","text_ar":"مَنْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing: (S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gave him"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a free gift."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamonaHu AlmaroA^apu wajohahaA AlmiroA=pa","text_ar":"تَمْنَحُ المَرْاَةُ وَجْهَهَا المِرْا=ةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The woman imparts somewhat of her beauty to the mirror:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"directs her face towards the mirror."},{"kind":"text","text":"And in like manner, accord. to some, you say, when you direct anything ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoSidu bihi","text_ar":"تَقْصِدُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") towards another thing,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaHotuhu A_iy~aAhu","text_ar":"مَنَحْتُهُ اـِيَّاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.)"}],"source_refs":["L","Lh","K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n38959","headword_ar":"مِنْحَةٌ","root":"mnH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A loan,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lending, of a she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat, that the person to whom the loan is granted may milk her for a certain period and then restore her to the lender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd:) [and in like manner,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maniyHapN","text_ar":"مَنِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minoHap","text_ar":"مِنْحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk; as a she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat that is given to another that he may milk her and afterwards restore her to the lender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minoHapN","text_ar":"مِنْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ewe"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-goat"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-camel, which her owner lends to a man that he may drink her milk and restore her when her milk ceases to flow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or both words signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat whose milk is given to another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-camel of which the soft hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabar","text_ar":"وَبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and milk and offspring are conceded by the owner to another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maniyHapN","text_ar":"مَنِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat that is lent for the sake of her milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minoHapN","text_ar":"مِنْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit which the lender thereof bestows upon the borrower."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, L.) The Arabs have four words which they use in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAriy~apN","text_ar":"عَارِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", viz. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maniyHapN","text_ar":"مَنِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariy~apN","text_ar":"عَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoqaArN","text_ar":"اـِفْقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ixobaAlN","text_ar":"اـِخْبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A'Obeyd, S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minoHapN mino layanK","text_ar":"مِنْحَةٌ مِنْ لَيَنٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Milch sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;) [app. meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are lent to a person"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minoHapN","text_ar":"مِنْحَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A loan"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land, and of money. (L.) ―         -b4-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing given;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maniyHapN","text_ar":"مَنِيحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a free gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minaHN","text_ar":"مِنَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) and pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maniyHapN","text_ar":"مَنِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAy^iHu","text_ar":"مَنَايِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","A","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}